      "body" : "@Martin That&#39;s not a problem with this code; rather, that&#39;s because Java interprets the leading zero as a signal that you&#39;re writing the number in octal instead of decimal: <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/specs/jls/se6/html/lexical.html#3.10.1\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">docs.oracle.com/javase/specs/jls/se6/html/lexical.html#3.10.&zwnj;&#8203;1</a> 1 * 8^2 + 2 * 8 + 3 = 8 * 10 + 3"
