    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>This is the method which i used to convert the integer to string.Correct me if i did wrong.</p>\n\n<pre><code>/**\n * @param a\n * @return\n */\nprivate String convertToString(int a) {\n\n    int c;\n    char m;\n    StringBuilder ans = new StringBuilder();\n    // convert the String to int\n    while (a &gt; 0) {\n        c = a % 10;\n        a = a / 10;\n        m = (char) ('0' + c);\n        ans.append(m);\n    }\n    return ans.reverse().toString();\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
